Harry Foster Welch https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Harry_Foster_Welch 0 Harry Foster Welch (November 27, 1893 – August 16, 1973) was an American radio and voice actor, best known for providing the voice of Popeye in cartoons and portraying the character in live performances beginning in 1934.
